query:
WITH ranked AS (
                        SELECT user_id, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY position) AS p
                        FROM krapbott_v2.queue
                        WHERE channel_id = $1
                    )
                    UPDATE krapbott_v2.queue q
                    SET position = ranked.p
                    FROM ranked
                    WHERE q.user_id = ranked.user_id AND q.channel_id = $1
